# Indonesia Store (IDR Only)

- **No Vercel middleware** — do not add `middleware.js` unless explicitly requested and tested on Vercel Preview
- **No `/id/` URL prefix** — all pages live at normal paths (`/products`, `/checkout`, etc.)
- **No IP-based or cookie-based market detection** — never worked reliably in production
- **Currency is always IDR** — enforced in `src/layouts/Layout.astro` and `lib/api/region-pricing.js`
- **Do not add** RegionSwitcher, dual-market docs, or geo redirect logic without explicit user request

Pricing reference: `docs/PRICING.md`
